# Claude Project Configuration

## Project: TaskFlow - Task Management Application

### Commit Message Policy (CRITICAL)
- NO AI attribution or branding in commit messages
- NO emojis in commit messages
- Use conventional commit format: `<type>: <description>`
- Examples: `feat: add feature`, `fix: resolve bug`, `refactor: improve code`
- Git hook enforces this policy at `.git/hooks/commit-msg`

### Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode
- Default exports for UI components
- Service layer pattern for business logic
- Custom hooks for state management

### Testing Before Commits
1. Run `npm run lint` - must pass with 0 errors/warnings
2. Run `npm run dev` - verify pages compile successfully
3. Test affected pages in browser

